     - Complete rewrite of comment sections with three prefix groups
     - `pcl-`: Paragraph hover highlight (`--bg-selection`), badge layer (absolute, pointer-events none), badge anchors, pill-shaped badges with glass morphism, amber glow on active
     - `cp-`: Backdrop with blur, card surface panel with modal shadow, header with count pill, editorial blockquote preview, amber scrollbar, warm empty state, input matching `cm-` patterns, pill submit button, chip reply indicator
     - `ccc-`: Cards with hover bg tint, thread lines with amber hover highlight, avatar rings with glow shadows, serif body text, pill action buttons
     - Mobile responsive breakpoints at 768px and 480px

   - **`server/sql/stories.sql`**
     - Added FK constraint for PostgREST join resolution:
     ```sql
