     - Moving mouse from paragraph to badge triggered `mouseleave` on paragraph, immediately setting `hoveredIndex` to null and unmounting badge
     - Fixed with 150ms debounced `leaveTimerRef` — paragraph mouseleave starts timer, badge anchor mouseenter cancels it

   - **Supabase FK error (user reported the URL and error message)**:
     - `story_comments.user_id` references `auth.users(id)` but PostgREST join `users(...)` needs FK to `public.users(id)`
     - Fix: SQL migration to add second FK to `public.users(id)`

   - **Field name mismatch**:
     - Frontend sent `{ body: "..." }` but backend controller extracts `req.body.comment`
     - `ChapterCommentCard` displayed `comment.body` but DB column is `comment`
     - Fixed both: CommentPanel sends `comment`, card displays `comment.comment`

   - **Badge flickering / can't click (CURRENT - user reported: "also the comment icon is flickering when i hove on it, i cant click it")**:
     - The 150ms debounce approach still causes mount/unmount cycles that create flicker
     - Not yet fixed — this is the pending task

5. Problem Solving:
   - Successfully implemented the full paragraph comment UI system from scratch
   - Resolved multiple hover interaction issues through iterative refinement
   - Fixed backend/frontend API field name mismatches
   - Identified and provided fix for Supabase PostgREST FK relationship issue
   - The flickering badge issue remains unsolved — the fundamental problem is that conditionally mounting/unmounting the badge based on hover state creates a race condition between the paragraph mouseleave and badge mouseenter events

6. All User Messages:
   - "Implement the following plan: [detailed paragraph-level comments plan]"
   - "how to add comments on paragraph? when i hover onto paragraph theres not comment icon to click"
   - "can you use /frontend-design to make it elegant and delightful and make sure it is visible during darkmode"
   - "why if i hove on the comment icon it disaappears"
