   Fix the flickering by always rendering all badge anchors in the DOM and controlling visibility through CSS classes (e.g., `.pcl-badge-anchor` with `opacity: 0; pointer-events: none` by default, adding a `.pcl-visible` class when hovered/has-comments to set `opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto`). This eliminates the mount/unmount cycle entirely. The user's exact quote: "also the comment icon is flickering when i hove on it, i cant click it"

